13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Pul o'tkazmalari kalkulyatori O'zbekistonga/dan pul jo'natish narxini komissiyalar va ayirboshlash kurslarini hisobga olgan holda hisoblaydi. O'zbekiston Markaziy Osiyoda pul o'tkazmalari oluvchi top-5 mamlakatga kiradi: yillik kiruvchi o'tkazmalar hajmi $10 mlrd dan oshadi, bu YaIMning sezilarli qismini tashkil etadi. Asosiy yo'nalishlar: Rossiya → O'zbekiston, Qozog'iston → O'zbekiston, Turkiya → O'zbekiston, BAA → O'zbekiston."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'tkazma tizimlari va komissiyalar (2025): Western Union — 1-3% (kichik summalar uchun $5 dan); MoneyGram — 1,5-3%; Zolotaya Korona (Koronapay) — 1-1,5% (Rossiyadan o'tkazmalar uchun eng mashhur); Contact — 1-2%; bank SWIFT — qat'iy $15-30; Uzum va Click orqali mobil o'tkazmalar — O'zbekiston ichida 0,5-1%. Yirik summalar ($1 000 dan ortiq) uchun bank SWIFT odatda umumiy xarajatlar bo'yicha foydaliroq."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Misol: mehnat migranti Rossiyadan O'zbekistonga $500 jo'natadi. Koronapay: komissiya ~$7 (1,4%), MB kursida ~$493 so'mda olinadi. Western Union: komissiya ~$12 (2,4%), ~$488 olinadi. Bank SWIFT: komissiya ~$25, ~$475 olinadi. Uzum Bank (karta→karta): komissiya ~$3 (0,6%) — ikkala bank kartasi mavjud bo'lganda eng foydali variant."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda o'tkazma olishda konvertatsiya kursini hisobga olish muhim: tijorat banklari O'zbekiston MB rasmiy kursidan 0,5-2% past kurs taklif etadi. Banklarning berilish punktlari ("}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ipoteka","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"Ipoteka"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" bank, Kapitalbank, NBU, Hamkorbank) orqali olish — pasport va o'tkazma kodi taqdim etilganda bepul. 100 mln so'm ekvivalentigacha naqd valyutani chegara orqali cheklovsiz olib o'tish mumkin, undan ortiq summa deklaratsiya qilinadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Saytimizda o'tkazmalar kalkulyatori barcha mavjud jo'natish usullarini narx, tezlik va qulaylik bo'yicha solishtiradi. Summa va yo'nalishni kiriting — kalkulyator har bir tizimning komissiyasini, olish uchun yakuniy summani va tavsiya etilgan usulni ko'rsatadi. Bu har bir o'tkazma uchun $5 dan $20 va undan ko'proq tejash imkonini beradi."}]]}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Ko'p beriladigan savollar"}],"$L18"]}],"$L19"]}]
